headline: Explosive device detonated next to IDF bulldozer in Gaza Strip
description: An explosive device was detonated next to an IDF bulldozer near a Jewish settlement in the southern Gaza Strip. No injuries or damage were reported. (Hanan Greenberg)
articleBody: An explosive device was detonated next to an IDF bulldozer near a Jewish settlement in the southern Gaza Strip. No injuries or damage were reported. (Hanan Greenberg)
title: ביקור בית: אצל מעצב האופנה דני מזרחי
